transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling Viagra. I can help you today.

Speaker 2: Hello. I received some Sildenafil in the mail today.

Speaker 1: I had ordered Viagra AGV and this came in its place.

Speaker 2: I currently have this product. I have Sildenafil already at home and I do not need more.

Speaker 1: What I wanted was the Viagra AGV.

Speaker 2: Just a quick thing. All Viagras are going to contain Sildenafil.

Speaker 1: The AGV just has the highest quality version of Sildenafil around which makes it an authorized generic.

Speaker 2: I know that. That is why I ordered it.

Speaker 1: I am just explaining to you that all Viagras have Sildenafil.

Speaker 2: I know that.

Speaker 1: I can take a look into your script to see what you received. What is your zip code?

Speaker 2: 12901.

Speaker 1: What is your last name?

Speaker 2: Walker.

Speaker 1: First name?

Speaker 2: Robert.

Speaker 1: Quick question. What does the engraving on the pill say on the ones you received?

Speaker 2: Sildenafil citrate 50 mg tablets.

Speaker 1: I will just say it one more time. The engraving on the pill.

Speaker 2: It says generic for Viagra.

Speaker 1: It is not going to say all that on the pill. I am asking you what the engraving on the pill says.

Speaker 2: Why would it be on the pill?

Speaker 1: I am asking you can you tell me what the pill says.

Speaker 2: The pill that is right in that little bottle you are reading. Take one out and tell me what that says.

Speaker 1: Hold on please.

Speaker 2: Thank you.

Speaker 1: Just a minute.

Speaker 2: It reads A339.

Speaker 1: It says A339 you said?

Speaker 2: AC339.

Speaker 1: Got it.

Speaker 2: You are breaking up. I can't hear you.

Speaker 1: I can hear you now. You were breaking up at first.

Speaker 2: Are you still there?

Speaker 1: I am still here and I will repeat.

Speaker 2: AC339.

Speaker 1: What I was telling you is that information I could confirm at the pharmacy did make a mistake.

Speaker 2: The only engraving you should have seen on your pill is 50 for the dosage.

Speaker 1: I am going to go ahead and let them know.

Speaker 2: They will ship you out a new order and you will get this in three to five business days.

Speaker 1: Aside from that, the one you have you are more than welcome to keep or dispose.

Speaker 2: We will send you the correct one.

Speaker 1: I want to make it clear.

Speaker 2: Once and for all I want the AGV.

Speaker 1: I just told you I would send that to you.

Speaker 2: I am not sure why you had to reiterate that.

Speaker 1: I want to make sure I get the right thing.

Speaker 2: I will send you that one.

Speaker 1: Thank you.

Speaker 2: No problem. Have a good one.

Speaker 1: Bye.
